{"tid":588409,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好頭痛，獨居老人同印傭相處問題...","createTime":"2018-03-11T07:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T01:09:46.000Z","uid":74908,"like":163,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"a1de473604ce28d6a7fb4136e9ecb754eabd27cc","tid":588409,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"長文抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，婆婆上年年尾中咗風<br />\n右半邊身活動能力差咗要人照顧同坐輪椅<br />\n上個月出院，因為公公早幾年瓜咗<br />\n其他人又要返工<br />\n佢自己一個住唯有搵個工人照顧佢<br />\n<br />\n搵咗個香港有10年以上經驗嘅印傭，貪佢識中文同照顧過中風老人家經驗<br />\n<br />\n平時睇佢就似正正常常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但婆婆見親個印印走開咗就開始r耳仔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話個印印中文不知幾咁好，識得串人窒佢<br />\n平時婆婆一個人生活好寧靜，電視都少睇<br />\n個印印就成日自己開電視睇cctvb<br />\n婆婆話細聲少少嘈住佢瞓，就唔講咁多即刻駁嘴<br />\n&ldquo;係喇係喇，我對耳冇你咁好聽唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n婆婆冇水食藥，叫佢幫手補水<br />\n就即刻拎起掃把扮掃地<br />\n&ldquo;咁急趕住去投胎咩！等等啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n（以上對話婆婆話如果係講大話佢自殺死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽到婆婆咁覺得好心痛，係咪應該裝個cam錄低佢哋生活好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be56677c7ff6d815973d681583d74b7488a084a","tid":588409,"uid":75753,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"換過個啦"},{"pid":"e060d19affb6bbb9705544645ac5b78b9969725e","tid":588409,"uid":52194,"like":175,"dislike":0,"score":175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:54:09.000Z","msg":"你係主人定個印係主人<br />\n裝cam backup定證據<br />\n炒人都易啲"},{"pid":"0932ea1a6a16a11df4d184a75a99e4e13c48d1c8","tid":588409,"uid":76883,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"個印傭最多係態度差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b3779f31305c